' FUNCTION:     ClearTable
' Description:  Deletes records from table
' Assumptions:  Table is in the current database (not linked)
' Parameters:   strTable - table name (string)
' Returns:      -
' Throws:       none
' References:   none
' Source/date:  Bonnie Campbell, May 27, 2015 - for NCPN tools
